node.text:
🌈 WE ARE GIVING AWAY THE WHOLE NEW COLLECTION 🌈

Love is love! Let's radiate this fantastic feeling with the brand new colorful aesthetic phone cases 📱✨

2 lucky winners will have an opportunity to win the whole Radiate Love collection. Yes, 8 phone cases 👀 How cool is that?

HOW TO ENTER:
1. Follow @burgaofficial
2. Like our 5 recent posts ❤
3. Tag your bestie who would also like to win the whole collection and put any colorful emoji 👇🏻

Giveaway starts at 18:00 (GMT+2) 14/08/21 until 18:00 (GMT+2) 23/08/2021. International giveaway, 14+ y.o participants only. 2 winners will be selected randomly and mentioned there. Odds of winning depend on the total number of entries received.

Instagram does not sponsor, endorse or administer this contest in any way, and there is no obligation between them. The information You provide will only be used as defined in these terms and conditions.

#burgaofficial #giveaway #radiatelove #newcollection
